{"tid":1186521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"博康邨兩男起爭執　一男持餐刀割傷對方逃逸","createTime":"2019-06-05T03:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T04:35:51.000Z","uid":6497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf0af3cbbbb357808cf3971c47029d5f749f0eea","tid":1186521,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190605/s00001/77cd767cb1cb26a8cb41f1840fe6f9c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190605%2Fs00001%2F77cd767cb1cb26a8cb41f1840fe6f9c3.jpg&h=32e181de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上8時42分，兩名男子於沙田博康邨商場一間茶餐廳食早餐期間，疑因瑣事起爭執，其中一人情緒激動，取刀𠝹傷對方腰部，逞兇後逃去無蹤。救護員到場，將事主送院治理，警方正調查事件，追緝兇徒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，傷者與兇徙素有積怨，今早於茶餐廳狹路相逢，其間兇徙一時情緒激動，隨手拾起枱面約一呎長餐刀傷人，事後未有結帳，帶著兇刀逃去無蹤。"},{"pid":"840ef01345fb1364f076258a12c1c4c029430553","tid":1186521,"uid":211935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"敗走"},{"pid":"c353462d9b3c10694a0fae24ea103cf5dedad5e7","tid":1186521,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"840ef01345fb1364f076258a12c1c4c029430553","tid":1186521,"uid":211935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"敗走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"食完早餐唔使埋單<br />\n點會係敗走"}]}